params.name: generated_outputs
params.description: The output of the model generate function. The output is expected to be a tensor of shape (batch_size, sequence_length)or (sequence_length,).

params.name: skip_special_tokens
params.description: Whether or not to remove special tokens in the output. Argument passed to the tokenizers batch_decode method.

params.name: Clean_up_tokenization_spaces
params.description: Whether or not to clean up the tokenization spaces. Argument passed to the tokenizers batch_decode method.

params.name: *kwargs
params.description: Additional arguments to be passed to the tokenizers batch_decode method.
